{"tid":583545,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本VS美國AV 為什麼這樣不同？","createTime":"2018-03-07T05:36:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-07T06:27:41.000Z","uid":3393,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c630b729bce8524f7c96370ac4a31e8256130ce9","tid":583545,"uid":3393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T05:36:27.000Z","msg":"美國跟日本這兩大色片出產地到底有什麼差別呢？根據《Smart FLASH》報導，自2003年始在美國色片廠商「Oriental Dream」工作的加藤 (假名) 透露，美國一年推出的色片只有約400-500部，每部發售量只有500-1500，但日本每年就推出超過3000部色片，日本的市場規模比美國大很多，但現在更多的人會買下載版、看線上串流。<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.teepr.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/a197d8e0fdec3a9d6f40f8f9448cd835.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.teepr.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F03%2Fa197d8e0fdec3a9d6f40f8f9448cd835.jpg&h=29c12fa8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n男女優方面，美國女優只有約200人，男優100人。美國沒有像日本一樣有素人色片，男女優大部份工作了10年以上，很多從20歲一直工作到35歲；男優的話，美國民眾都比較愛看巨GG。<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.teepr.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/0b52e360261985b1e015af509be283d2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.teepr.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F03%2F0b52e360261985b1e015af509be283d2.jpg&h=3944aa51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n色片製作費一直在減少，目前要製作一部色片的話，約需要花費300萬日元 (約83萬新台幣)，而美國女.優的報酬則是約15萬日元 (約4萬新台幣)，流程為：花1小時化妝，1小時拍照，30分鐘啪啪啪，這樣一天就可以拍出好幾部。由於演出費不高、拍攝時間緊迫，美國色片通常都會由很多人出演一部作品，而不像日本是一人一部。<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.teepr.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/b46a4526a5240885bd43828afcc86604.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.teepr.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F03%2Fb46a4526a5240885bd43828afcc86604.jpg&h=03e98b6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國色片市場比日本小很多，一部2小時的色片通常賣30-40美元 (約900-1200新台幣)。日本推出色片時，總會讓女.優進行簽名會，而事實上美國女.優也一樣，也會舉辦見面活動，像是登上《花花公子雜誌》等，讓曝光的機會更多。<br />\n<br />\n延伸推薦：不高潮女優 VS 自慰棒：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4_BbtxXxTRU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4_BbtxXxTRU&d=rBBbksJCFdB8J9VfulbnZ%2BPnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=a394876f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4_BbtxXxTRU</a><br />\n<br />\n參考資料：Smart FLASH"},{"pid":"69d279e913d60c644db4489a66da2f23f5d65bf0","tid":583545,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T05:38:47.000Z","msg":"男女優方面，美國女優只有約200人，男優100人。美國沒有像日本一樣有素人色片，男女優大部份工作了10年以上<br />\nOrly"},{"pid":"29b6a24f695e38270f561626f54d26d7818655cd","tid":583545,"uid":70629,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T05:40:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/dte_BbtmKt4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fdte_BbtmKt4&d=rBBbksJCFdB8J9VfulbnZ%2BPnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=90c6cefd\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/dte_BbtmKt4</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ca23c757f406ec35190dc5d080ac3d9fbec8298","tid":583545,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T05:40:54.000Z","msg":"鬼妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"613a459d4521d7c5c71cabbc75285bde8e7f8574","tid":583545,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T05:41:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b34a8881eecfeb9c58bacd949e50b173148e8a6","tid":583545,"uid":8048,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T05:41:35.000Z","msg":"硬係覺得鬼佬片好暴力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35b7087acc2cbbd13c52fd2c3b6767c3b7fd56d6","tid":583545,"uid":25345,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T05:43:03.000Z","msg":"鬼片好悶<br />\n女成日 o yes o come on<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n日本既凌虐 阿伯片正好多"},{"pid":"1344b2a5bd9756cc863a13444cbc842b0b7ceca0","tid":583545,"uid"